text: Réka Hagymási (born 29 July 1993) is a Hungarian sprint canoeist.Profile She won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian female canoeists Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:Canoeists from Budapest
